==English==

===Noun Phrase===
'''bovine spongiform encephalopathy'''

A fatal, neurodegenerative disease of cattle, which is transmissable to humans through misshaped prion proteins, usually in an epidemic fashion, originated from the [[United Kingdom]].  Abbreviation: BSE.

